Augustus Neville https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Augustus_Neville 0 Augustus Neville was a New Zealand-born actor who appeared in a number of the early films for director Raymond Longford but was best known for his stage career in Australia, particularly in works by William Shakespeare. He worked for many years with Alfred Dampier and Allan Wilkie.
